azy Rhythms]]'' || [[The Feelies]] ||\n|-\n| ''Give 'Em Hell'' || [[Witchfynde]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Growing Up in Public (Lou Reed album)|Growing Up in Public]]'' || [[Lou Reed]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Holiday '80]]'' || [[The Human League]] || EP\n|-\n| ''[[Just One Night (Eric Clapton album)|Just One Night]]'' || [[Eric Clapton]] || Live\n|-\n| ''[[Lookin' for Trouble]]'' || [[Toronto (band)|Toronto]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Marauder (Magnum album)|Marauder]]'' || [[Magnum (band)|Magnum]] || Live\n|-\n| ''[[Middle Man (album)|Middle Man]]'' || [[Boz Scaggs]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Ska 'n' B]]'' || [[Bad Manners]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sky 2 (album)|Sky 2]]'' || [[Sky (band)|Sky]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Snakes and Ladders (Gerry Rafferty album)|Snakes and Ladders]]'' || [[Gerry Rafferty]] ||\n|-\n| ''Tommy Tutone'' || [[Tommy Tutone]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Waters Edge]]'' || [[The Sweet|Sweet]] ||\n|}\n\n===May===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Day\n!Album\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |5\n| ''[[Totale's Turns]]'' || [[The Fall (band)|The Fall]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Wheels of Steel]]'' || [[Saxon (band)|Saxon]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |8\n| ''[[The Golden Years (EP)|The Golden Years]]'' || [[Mot\u00f6rhead]] || EP\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |9\n| ''[[Bass Culture]]'' || [[Linton Kwesi Johnson]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Warm Leatherette (album)|Warm Leatherette]]'' || [[Grace Jones]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |13\n| ''[[21 at 33]]'' || [[Elton John]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |16\n| ''[[Freedom of Choice (album)|Freedom of Choice]]'' || [[Devo]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[McCartney II]]'' || [[Paul McCartney]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |17\n| ''[[Bad Reputation (Joan Jett album)|Bad Reputation]]'' || [[Joan Jett]] || Self-titled album released in 1980. Re-released as Bad Reputation in Jan 1981\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |20\n| ''[[Unmasked (Kiss album)|Unmasked]]'' || [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |22\n| ''[[Diana (album)|Diana]]'' || [[Diana Ross]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" |23\n| ''[[Flesh and Blood (Roxy Music album)|Flesh and Blood]]'' || [[Roxy Music]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Peter Gabriel (1980 album)|Peter Gabriel]]'' || [[Peter Gabriel]] || Third Album\n|-\n|''[[Travelogue (The Human League album)|Travelogue]]'' || [[The Human League]] || Second Album\n|-\n|''[[The Up Escalator]]'' || [[Graham Parker]] || \n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |28\n| ''[[Tight Shoes]]'' || [[Foghat]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\" |31\n| ''[[Ready an' Willing]]'' || [[Whitesnake]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"15\" align=\"center\" |?\n| ''[[Can't Stop the Music (album)|Can't Stop the Music]]'' || [[Village People]] || Soundtrack\n|- \n| ''[[The Correct Use of Soap]]'' || [[Magazine (band)|Magazine]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[I Just Can't Stop It]]'' || [[The Beat (British band)|The Beat]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Magic of Boney M. \u2013 20 Golden Hits]]'' || [[Boney M.]] || Compilation\n|-\n| ''[[Music Man (album)|Music Man]]'' || [[Waylon Jennings]] ||\n|-\n| ''Quicksand Shoes'' || [[Streetheart (band)|Streetheart]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Roses in the Snow]]'' || [[Emmylou Harris]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Songs the Lord Taught Us]]'' || [[The Cramps]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Sportscar (album)|Sportscar]]'' || [[Judy Tzuke]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Suicide: Alan Vega and Martin Rev]]'' || [[Suicide (band)|Suicide]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Tangram (album)|Tangram]]'' || [[Tangerine Dream]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Tale of the Tape]]'' || [[Billy Squier]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Three Mantras]]'' || [[Cabaret Voltaire (band)|Cabaret Voltaire]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[What's the Word]]'' || [[The Fabulous Thunderbirds]] ||\n|-\n| ''Woman Love'' || [[Burton Cummings]] ||\n|}\n\n===June===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Day\n!Album\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |2\n| ''[[Found All the Parts]]'' || [[Cheap Trick]] || EP\n|-\n| ''[[I'm a Rebel]]'' || [[Accept (band)|Accept]] ||\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |4\n| ''[[East (Cold Chisel album)|East]]'' || [[Co