ydream Believer#Anne Murray version|Daydream Believer]]\" \u2013 [[Anne Murray]]\n*\"[[Deep Inside My Heart]]\" \u2013 [[Randy Meisner]] with [[Kim Carnes]]\n*\"[[Deja Vu (Dionne Warwick song)|Deja Vu]]\" \u2013 [[Dionne Warwick]]\n*\"[[Desire (Bee Gees song)#Andy Gibb version|Desire]]\" \u2013 [[Andy Gibb]]\n*\"[[Don't Ask Me Why (Billy Joel song)|Don't Ask Me Why]]\" \u2013 [[Billy Joel]]\n*\"[[Don't Do Me Like That]]\" \u2013 [[Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers]]\n*\"[[Don't Fall in Love with a Dreamer]]\" \u2013 [[Kenny Rogers]] and [[Kim Carnes]]\n*\"Don't Let Go\" \u2013 [[Isaac Hayes]]\n*\"[[Dreamin' (Cliff Richard song)|Dreamin']]\" \u2013 [[Cliff Richard]] (charted in 1981 in U.S.)\n*\"[[Drivin' My Life Away]]\" \u2013 [[Eddie Rabbitt]]\n*\"[[Emotional Rescue (song)|Emotional Rescue]]\" \u2013 [[The Rolling Stones]]\n*\"[[Entre Nous (Rush song)|Entre Nous]]\" \u2013 [[Rush (band)|Rush]]\n*\"[[Even It Up]]\" \u2013 [[Heart (band)|Heart]]\n*\"Even The Score\" \u2013 [[Toronto (band)|Toronto]]\n*\"[[Fame (Irene Cara song)|Fame]]\" \u2013 [[Irene Cara]]\n*\"Fashion Victim\" \u2013 [[Rough Trade (band)|Rough Trade]]\n*\"[[Fire Lake]]\" \u2013 [[Bob Seger|Bob Seger and The Silver Bullet Band]]\n*\"[[Freewill (song)|Freewill]]\" \u2013 [[Rush (band)|Rush]]\n*\"[[Gee Whiz (Look at His Eyes)|Gee Whiz]]\" \u2013 [[Bernadette Peters]]\n*\"[[Give Me the Night (George Benson song)|Give Me the Night]]\" \u2013 [[George Benson]]\n*\"[[He's So Shy]]\" \u2013 [[The Pointer Sisters]] \n*\"[[Heartbreaker (Pat Benatar song)|Heartbreaker]]\" \u2013 [[Pat Benatar]]\n*\"[[Hello America (song)|Hello America]]\" \u2013 [[Def Leppard]]\n*\"[[Her Strut]]\" \u2013 [[Bob Seger|Bob Seger & The Silver Bullet Band]]\n*\"Hidin' From Love\" \u2013 [[Bryan Adams]]\n*\"[[High School Confidential (Rough Trade song)|High School Confidential]]\" \u2013 [[Rough Trade (band)|Rough Trade]]\n*\"[[Him (Rupert Holmes song)|Him]]\" \u2013 [[Rupert Holmes]]\n*\"[[How Do I Make You]]\" \u2013 [[Linda Ronst